				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				One last piece of info:<BR>
<BR>
Heady Kiola Recipe<BR>
<BR>
2 packets of kiola sap<BR>
1 flask of water (purchased, not summoned)<BR>
1 bottle<BR>
<BR>
Combine ingredients in a brew barrel.<BR>
<BR>
These go trivial at 46 but but unless you get your brewing skill several points higher than that you will still have many failures.
				</font>
